title: Trade, Impeachment, Marianne Williamson
itunes:title: Trade, Impeachment, Marianne Williamson
description:
Panel: Jason Rosenbaum, Founder of Seward Square Strategies, former Digital Ads Director for the Hilary Clinton presidential campaign and Tyler Deaton, Republican strategist and fundraiser, President of Allegiance Strategies.


Kevin also discussed the 2020 race, impeachment and healthcare with Democratic Presidential candidate Marianne Williamson.
